dct_title_s: A map of the United States : compiled chiefly from the state maps and other authentic information
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures. Appears in Mathew Carey's General atlas. Philadelphia. 1796? Prime meridians: London and Philadelphia. Includes inset of Florida and the northern gulf coast west to New Orleans. Historic Maps copy has some place names added in ms.
dct_publisher_sm: Philadelphia : Engraved for and sold by Matthew Carey, 1795.
